text: Alakamisy is a town in Fianarantsoa Province in central Madagascar. ==Geography== Nearby towns include Ambohimirana, Andoharano, Andranoraikitra, Antsahamalaza, Fandrianakely, Morarano, Tsarazaza and Vohibolo. ==Economy== There is a mine in the vicinity of the town named the Alakamisy Itenina Mine. The mine is worked in alluvium and was discovered in 1989 in a rice plantation.Ggems.com ==References== Category:Populated places in Fianarantsoa Province
title: Alakamisy, Fianarantsoa
